subsection.text:
Not later than 90 days after the date of the enactment of this Act, the Secretary of State shall submit to the appropriate congressional committees a report that details actions taken by the Department of State through the Department of State rewards program (
              22 U.S.C. 2708
            ) to obtain information on fundraising, financing, and money laundering activities of Hezbollah and its agents and affiliates.

